name: You Go Girl
description:
18 FREE png illustrations of women, girls and kids!


Every occasion is for me a joy to celebrate women and the constant work all of us are doing to live in an equal society.


This week the collection of free illustrations is dedicated to all of the beautiful, strong and accomplished women, girls and baby girls out there


Time was not enough to include many characters, but I'm going to complete this set in the next weeks!
